BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:RjilSRED204hBmilrL0r9
SUMMARY:Maye & Ambar Lucid
DTSTAMP:20260326T215650Z
DTSTART:20260504T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Entre Dos Mundos brings together maye and Ambar Lucid for a tou
	r rooted in duality\; not just sonically\, but also emotionally. Together\
	, they create a space that feels both intimate and expansive\, where softn
	ess\, healing\, and self-expression take center stage.Framed as a space to
	 unmask and reconnect\, the tour leans into themes of vulnerability and th
	e divine feminine\, inviting audiences to tap into a more instinctive and 
	emotional side of themselves. While maye and Ambar come from distinct arti
	stic worlds\, their contrast is what defines the experience: two energies 
	in conversation\, balancing light and shadow in real time.\nAll sales are 
	final. There are no refunds unless the event is cancelled or postponed Ope
	ning Acts are subject to change or cancelation at any time without notice.
